; Regression test for issue #793
; Verify that custom streambuf implementations work correctly for expression
; parsing from strings (ptrinbuf) and formatted output.  The original issue
; concerned portability of sputc/overflow/xsputn in custom streambuf classes;
; the affected output streambuf (pyoutbuf) was fixed and later removed.
; This test confirms that string-based expression parsing — which exercises
; the remaining ptrinbuf input streambuf — produces correct results.

2024/01/15 Groceries
    Expenses:Food             $42.50
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/20 Gas Station
    Expenses:Transport        $35.00
    Assets:Checking

test reg --format '%(format_date(date, "%Y-%m-%d")) %(payee) %(scrub(display_amount))\n'
2024-01-15 Groceries $42.50
2024-01-15 Groceries $-42.50
2024-01-20 Gas Station $35.00
2024-01-20 Gas Station $-35.00
end test

test bal --format '%(account) %(scrub(display_total))\n'
Assets:Checking $-77.50
Expenses $77.50
Expenses:Food $42.50
Expenses:Transport $35.00
 0
end test
